                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17882276" author="mapohl" created="Tue, 17 Sep 2024 07:08:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=becket_qin&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;becket_qin&quot;&gt;becket_qin&lt;/a&gt; can you have a look at this? On more general terms, the community agreed on not adding timeouts to the unit tests. If a test runs into a deadlock, Flink&apos;s CI would produce a thread dump in the end that might help with the root cause analysis. Adding a @Timeout to the test prevents us from getting this thread dump.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17883214" author="JIRAUSER306704" created="Fri, 20 Sep 2024 10:08:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://dev.azure.com/apache-flink/apache-flink/_build/results?buildId=62290&amp;amp;view=logs&amp;amp;j=2e8cb2f7-b2d3-5c62-9c05-cd756d33a819&amp;amp;t=2dd510a3-5041-5201-6dc3-54d310f68906&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://dev.azure.com/apache-flink/apache-flink/_build/results?buildId=62290&amp;amp;view=logs&amp;amp;j=2e8cb2f7-b2d3-5c62-9c05-cd756d33a819&amp;amp;t=2dd510a3-5041-5201-6dc3-54d310f68906&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17883558" author="showuon" created="Sat, 21 Sep 2024 23:22:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Opened a PR to remove the timeout first: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/25371&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/25371&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17883964" author="becket_qin" created="Mon, 23 Sep 2024 17:11:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=showuon&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;showuon&quot;&gt;showuon&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mapohl&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mapohl&quot;&gt;mapohl&lt;/a&gt; . I was trying to reproduce the issue by removing the timeout and set the close timeout to Long.MAX_VALUE. I did not see a failure in over 30K runs. But it looks like some test run can take a bit longer than other runs. At this point, it looks like this is more of a flaky test instead of real issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17885129" author="becket_qin" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2024 18:27:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Merged to master.&lt;/p&gt;

